column3: LaTeX<ref>This refers to the direct output of raw LaTeX (often in a format similar to the BibTeX-generated .bbl files). Many programs can export BibTeX (see above table)  which can then be processed into LaTeX.</ref>
<ref>Database can be exported as a whole in BibTeX format. Text (ie. thoughts  comments  and quotations) can be fed into a number of TeX editors in LaTeX code or UTF-8 </ref>
<ref>Database can be exported as a whole in BibTeX format.Insert citations via citation key generated by Mendeley  </ref>
